                these may seem unimaginable to adults.<br/>
                A more detailed data is this: according to a national census conducted by Tencent, 40% of the more than 200 million children
                own pocket money of more than 1,000 yuan. Going up to first-tier cities in the north, more than 50% of children have pocket
                money of up to 10,000 yuan. However, only 24% of children manage pocket money effectively.
            </p>
            <p class="center">
